{"id":104491,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/09/简讯：美与沙特达成最大宗武器交易/","date":"2010-09-14T15:39:18Z","modified":"2010-09-14T15:39:18Z","title":"简讯：美与沙特达成最大宗武器交易","content":"<div>\n<p>来自华盛顿的消息说，美国将出售沙特价值高达600亿美元武器装备，这将是美国达成的最大宗武器交易。</p>\n<p>出售的武器包括先进的战斗机和武装直升机。这一交易细节尚不清楚，仍需得到国会的批准。</p>\n<p>BBC在华盛顿的记者说，国会不大会否决这一协议，因为通过支持盟国沙特可以遏制来自伊朗的威胁。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/4mVaJkBR1FmS7mKSsJyFJvsxo4U/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/4mVaJkBR1FmS7mKSsJyFJvsxo4U/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/4mVaJkBR1FmS7mKSsJyFJvsxo4U/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/4mVaJkBR1FmS7mKSsJyFJvsxo4U/1/di\"></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=EzotIebubIg:dI3fO9ZpJUA:mqyYa2mfVbY\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=mqyYa2mfVbY\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=EzotIebubIg:dI3fO9ZpJUA:PFx2F_oWK34\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=PFx2F_oWK34\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=EzotIebubIg:dI3fO9ZpJUA:DUWcskeyX7o\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=DUWcskeyX7o\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=EzotIebubIg:dI3fO9ZpJUA:clraHZBW0_I\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=clraHZBW0_I\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=EzotIebubIg:dI3fO9ZpJUA:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?a=EzotIebubIg:dI3fO9ZpJUA:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/cnbbc?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/EzotIebubIg\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p>请看原文：<br />\n<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwe